---
import { SITE } from '~/lib/data';
---

<div class="flex h-full flex-col gap-3">
  <header class="flex items-start justify-between">
    <h3 class="font-mono text-sm font-medium text-foreground">about</h3>
    <span class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase text-muted">{SITE.location}</span>
  </header>

  <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
    <div
      class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-accent/40 bg-accent/10 font-display text-sm font-semibold text-accent"
    >
      MK
    </div>
    <div>
      <p class="text-sm font-medium text-foreground">{SITE.author}</p>
      <p class="font-mono text-[11px] text-muted">senior full-stack</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <p class="mt-auto text-xs leading-relaxed text-muted">
    I ship the boring infrastructure that keeps things alive: state machines, retries, ledgers,
    cascade boundaries. Then I make the demo move.
  </p>
</div>
